data.description: Welcome to this beautiful split level home located in Snellville, GA. This charming home offers a perfect blend of comfort and style. Step inside to discover elegant white cabinetry and stainless steel appliances, including a stove, oven, and dishwasher. The open sitting dining area is flooded with natural light, creating a welcoming space for gatherings or family meals. The luxurious master bedroom boasts ample space to accommodate a king-size bed, ensuring a restful retreat. A convenient laundry area is ready to accommodate side-by-side washer and dryer units. Hardwood flooring throughout the main living areas adds a touch of elegance, while cozy carpeting in the bedrooms enhances comfort. Don't miss out on the opportunity to make this your new home sweet home! Schedule a viewing today.
